              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Supply Chain Management</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              End-to-end supply chain solutions that optimize efficiency, reduce costs, and improve delivery times for your business.
